data.description:
Welcome to this delightful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Bixby, OK, where comfort and style meet. The 3-car garage boasts a rare 4ft extension, providing ample space for all your needs. Step onto the covered patio, perfect for morning coffee or evening relaxation.

Inside, discover a spacious 4th bedroom with barn doors and an oversized closet. The kitchen features the largest island and cabinets in a Simmons home, complemented by granite countertops and a beautiful backsplash. Vaulted ceilings with wood beams add character to the living space.

A hall behind the kitchen leads to two bedrooms and a secondary bath, with a convenient mudroom or desk space. The laundry room is well-equipped for efficiency. High-end vinyl flooring graces the entire home, except for the children's room.

The master bedroom includes additional square footage in the bath area and an upgraded closet for seasonal storage. The covered back patio, extended with extra concrete, invites outdoor enjoyment. The garage is a standout feature with recessed lighting, making it the largest in the neighborhood.

This property is not only a spacious haven but also part of a phenomenal community with a pool, walking trails, and proximity to the brand new Bixby West Elementary. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home!
